hadiths[41]{hadithnumber,text}:
4163,"Abdullaah-bin-Muslima bin Qanab ne hamein hadis bayan ki : hamein Malik-bin-Anas ne Zaid-bin-Aslam se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Allah ki raah mein (jihad karne ke liye kisi ko) aik umda ghodey par Sawar kya ( usey de diyaa) to iske ( naey ( Malik ne usey zaaye kar diya (uski theek tarah se khabargeeri na ki) , maine khayal kya ke wo usey kam qeemat par farokht kar dega, chunanche maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske barey mein puchha to aap ne farmaya : usey mat khareedo aur na apna (diya hua) sadqa wapas lo kyonke sadqa wapas leney wala aisey kuttey ki tarah hai jo qai (chaatney ke liye) uski taraf laut-taa hai."
4164,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne hamein Malik-bin-Anas se isi sanad ke sath (ye ( hadis bayan ki aur izafa kya : usey mat khareedo , chahey wo usey tum ko aik dirham mein de.'"
4165,"Rooh bin-Qasim ne hamein Zaid-bin-Aslam se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Allah ki raah mein aik ghoda sawari ke taur par diya, to unhon-ne usey uske Malik ke yahan us haal mein paya ke usne usey zaaye kar diya tha aur wo tang dast tha, chunanche unhon (Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu)) ne usey kharidney ka irada kya, wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aapko ye baat batai to aap ne farmaya : usey mat khareedo , chahey wo tumhen aik dirham mein diya jaey, sadqa wapas leney waley ki misal us kuttey ke jaisi hai jo apni qai mein lot jata hai) chaat-taa hai.)"
4166,"Sufiyan ne Zaid-bin-Aslam se isi sanad ke sath ( yahi ( hadis bayan ki, albatta Malik aur Rooh ki hadis zyada mukammal aur zyada ( mufassal ( hai."
4167,"Imam Malik ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne Allah ki raah mein aik ghoda sawari ke taur par diya, phir unhon-ne usey us haalat mein paya ke usko farokht kya ja raha tha, unhon-ne usey kharidney ka irada kya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske barey mein poochha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey mat khareedo aur (kabhi) apna sadqa wapas na lo."
4168,"Lais-bin-Sad aur Ubaidullah donon ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Malik ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki."
4169,"Salim ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Allah ki raah mein sawari ke liye aik ghoda diya, phir unhon-ne usey dekha ke farokht kya ja raha hai. to unhon-ne usko kharidney ka irada kar liya, phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey umr ! apna sadqa wapas mat lo."
4170,"Esa-bin-Yonus ne hamein khabar di : hamein Auzai ne abu-Jafar Muhammad-bin Ali se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne ibne-Musaiyab se, unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya is shakhs ki misal jo sadqa wapas leta hai us kuttey ki tarah hai jo qai karta hai, phir apni qai ki taraf laut-ta hai aur khata hai."
4171,"ibne-Mubarak ne hamein Auzai se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : maine (abu-Jafar) Muhammad-bin (Zainul-Aabedeen ( Ali-bin Husain (Rahmatullahi-alaih) se suna, wo isi sanad se isi tarah bayan kar rahe they."
4172,"Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir ne hamein hadis bayan ki : mujhey Abdur-Rehman bin-Amr ne hadis bayan ki ke unhein Fatima binte-rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke bete (padpotey), Muhammad (al-Baqar) ne ye hadis isi sanad ke sath unhi ki hadis ki tarah bayan ki."
4173,"Bukair se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna is shakhs ki misal jo sadqa karta hai, phir apne sadqey ko wapas ley leta hai us kuttey ki tarah hai jo qai karta hai phir apni qai khata hai."
4174,"Shoba ne hamein hadis bayan ki : maine Qatada se suna, wo Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se hadis bayan kar rahe they, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : apne hiba ko wapas leney wala apni qai ki taraf lotney waley ki tarah hai."
4175,Saeed ne Qatada se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
4176,"Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : apna hiba wapas leney wala kuttey ki tarah hai jo qai karta hai, phir apni qai ki taraf laut-ta hai."
4177,"Imam Malik ne ibne-Shahab se aur unhon-ne Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman aur Muhammad-bin Noman-bin-Bashir se riwayat ki, wo donon Hazrat Noman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kar rahe they ke unhon-ne kaha : unke walid unhein lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur kaha : maine apne us betey ko ghulam tohfey mein diya hai jo mera tha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tum ne apne sab bachchon ko us jaisa tohfa diya hai? unhon-ne kaha : nahi, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey wapas lo."
4178,"Ibrahim bin Sad ne hamein ibne-Shahab se khabar di, unhon-ne Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman aur Muhammad-bin Nauman se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Noman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mere walid mujhey lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur kaha : maine apne is betey ko aik ghulam tohfey mein diya hai. to aap ne puchha : kya tum ne apne sab beton ko) aisa ( tohfa diya hai? unhon-ne jawab diya : nahi. aap ne farmaya : usey wapas lo."
4179,"ibne-Uena, Lais-bin-Sad, Yunus aur Mamar sab ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, albatta Yunus aur Mamar ki hadis mein tamam beton ko ke alfaz hain aur Leis aur ibne-Uena ki hadis mein tamam aulad ko hai aur Muhammad-bin Nauman aur Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman se riwayat ki hui Leis ki riwayat ( yun ( hai ke Hazrat Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) (apne betey ( Nauman (Raziallahu anhu) ko lekar aaey."
4180,"Urwa se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Hazrat Noman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : unke walid ne unhein aik ghulam diya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse puchha : ye kaisa ghulam hai? unhon-ne kaha : ye mere walid ne mujhey diya hai. ( phir (aap ne ( Nauman (Raziallahu anhu) ke walid se) puchha : tum ne iske tamam bhaiyon ko bhi isi tarah Atiya diya hai jaisey usko diya hai? unhon-ne jawab diya : nahi. aap ne farmaya : usey wapas lo."
4181,"Husain ne Shabi se, unhon-ne Hazrat Noman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mere walid ne apne maal mein se mujhey hiba kya ( yahan sadqa hiba ke mana mein hai) to meri walida Umra binte-Rawaha (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main razi nahi hungi yahan tak ke tum Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko gawah bana lo. mere walid mujhey lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey taake aapko mujh par kiye gaey sadqa ( hiba ( par gawah banaaein . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse puchha : kya tum ne ye ( sulook ( apne tamam bachchon ke sath kya hai? unhon-ne jawab diya : nahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum sab Allah se daro aur apne bachchon ke beech adl karo. chunanche mere walid wapas aaey aur wo sadqa ( hiba ( wapas ley liya."
4182,"abu-Hayyan Taimi ne hamein Shabi se hadis bayan ki : mujhey Hazrat Noman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke unki walida , ( Umra ( binte- Rawaha ne unke walid se, unke maal mein se, apne betey ke liye ( baagh , zamin wghaira) kuchh hiba kiye janey ka mutalba kya, unhon-ne usey aik saal tak thande bastey mein daaley rakha, phir unhein ( iska ( khayal aaya to unhon ( walida ( ne kaha : main razi nahi hungi yahan tak ke tum us par, jo tum ne mere betey ke liye hiba kya hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko gawah bana lo. is par mere walid ne mera hath thaama, main un dinon bachcha tha, aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! uski walida binte-Rawaha ko ye pasand hai ke main aapko us cheez par gawah banaun jo maine iske betey ko di hai, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : Bashir ! kya iske siwa bhi tumharey bachchey hain? unhon-ne jawab diya : ji haan! aap ne puchha : kya un sab mein se har aik ko tum ne isi tarah hiba kya hai? unhon-ne jawab diya : nahi aap ne farmaya : phir mujhey gawah na banao, main zulm par gawah nahi banta.'"
4183,"Ismail ne hamein Shabi se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Noman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya iske siwa bhi tumharey betey hain? unhon-ne kaha : ji haan. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : kya un sab ko bhi tum ne us jaisa Atiya diya hai? unhon-ne jawab diya : nahi. aap ne farmaya : to main zulm par gawah nahi banta ."
4184,Aasim ahwal ne Shabi se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Noman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke walid se farmaya : mujhey zulm par gawah mat banao .
4185,"Daawood-bin-abii-Hind ne Shabi se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Noman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mere walid mujhey uthaey huey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! gawah rahen ke maine Nauman ko apne maal mein se itna itna diya hai. aap ne farmaya : kya tum ne apne sab beton ko usi jaisa Atiya diya hai jaisa tum ne Nauman ko diya hai? unhon-ne jawab diya : nahi. aap ne farmaya : is par mere siwa kisi aur ko gawah banao . phir farmaya : kya tumhen ye baat achi lagti hai ke wo sab tumharey sath neki (husne sulook) karne mein barabar hun? unhon-ne kaha : kyon nahi ! aap ne farmaya : to phir (tum bhi aisa ( na karo."
4186,"Ibne-Aun ne hamein Shabi se, unhon-ne Hazrat Noman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mere walid ne mujhey aik tohfa diya, phir mujhey lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey taake aapko gawah banaaein. aap ne puchha : kya tum ne apne sab bachchon ko ye (usi tarah ka ( tohfa diya hai? unhon-ne jawab diya : nahi. aap ne puchha : kya tum un sabse isi tarah ka nek sulook nahi chahtey jis tarah us ( betey) se chahtey ho? unhon-ne jawab diya : kyon nahi ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : to main (zulm par) gawah nahi banta. (kyonke us amal ki bina par pahley tumhari taraf se aur phir jawaaban unki taraf se zulm hoga. Ibne-Aun ne kaha : maine ye hadis Muhammad (bin Sirin ( ko sunai to unhon-ne kaha : mujhey bayan kya gaya hai ke aap ne farmaya : apne beton ke darmyan yaksaaniyat munasib rakho ( lafzi mana hain : taqriban aik jaisa sulook yani unko is baat ka aadi banao.)"
4187,"Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi ne kaha : mere betey ko apna ghulam hiba kar do aur mere liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko gawah banao . wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur kaha : falan ki beti ne mujh se mutalba kya hai ke main iske betey ko apna ghulam hiba kar dun aur us ne kaha hai : mere liye (us par) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko gawah banao . to aap ne puchha : kya iske aur bhai hain? unhon-ne jawab diya : ji haan. aap ne puchha : kya un sab ko bhi tum ne isi tarah Atiya diya hai jis tarah usey diya hai? unhon-ne jawab diya : nahi. aap ne farmaya : ye durust nahi aur main sirf haq par gawah banta hun."
4188,"Imam Malik ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis aadmi ko umr bhar ke liye di janey wali cheez iske aur uski aulad ke liye di gaee to wo usi ki hai jisey di gaee, wo us shakhs ko wapas nahi milegi jisne di thi, kyonke us ne aisa Atiya diya hai jis mein wiraasat jari ho gaee hai."
4189,"Leis ne hamein ibne-Shahab se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Salma se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : jisne kisi shakhs ko umr bhar ke liye Atiya diya ke wo iska aur uski aulad ka hai to uski is baat ne, us cheez mein, iske haq ko khatm kar diya aur wo usi ki hai jisey umr bhar ke liye di gaee aur uski aulad ki. magar Yahya ne, apni hadis ke shuruat hi mein kaha : jis shakhs ke umr bhar ke liye Atiya diya gaya to wo usi ka aur uski aulad ka hai."
4190,"ibne-Juraij ne hamein khabar di : mujhey ibne-Shahab ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ki hadis ki ro se umra aur uske tareeqey ke barey mein bataya ke unhein Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis aadmi ne kisi doosrey shakhs ko umr bhar ke liye tohfa diya ke wo iska aur uski aulad ka hai aur kaha : maine tumhen aur tumhari aulad ko diya jab tak tum mein se koi zinda hai, to wo usi ka hai jisey diya gaya hai aur wo iske (pahley ( Malik ko wapas nahi hoga kyonke us ne aisa Atiya diya hai jis mein wiraasat jari ho gaee hai."
4191,"Mamar ne hamein Zohri (Rehmatullahi-alaih) Mina se khabar di, unhon-ne abu-Salma se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : wo umra jisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Nafiz kya ye hai ke aadmi kahey : ye tumharey liye aur tumhari aulad ke liye hai, albatta jab wo kahey : ye tumharey liye hai jab tak tum zinda ho, to wo uskey Malik ko wapas mil jaeyga Mamar ne kaha : imam Zohri (Rehmatullahi-alaih) Mina usi ke mutabiq fatwa detey they."
4192,"ibne-abi-Ze-ib ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us shakhs ke barey mein faisla kya jisey umr bhar ke liye (ye keh kar) Atiya diya gaya ke wo iska aur uski aulad ka hai to wo hutami taur par usi ka hoga, is ( sura ( mein dene waley ke liye koi shart lagaana aur istisnaa karna jaaiz nahi. abu-Salma ne kaha : kyonke us ne aisa Atiya diya hai jis mein wiraasat jari ho chuki hai to wiraasat ne uski shart ko khatm kar diya."
4193,"Khalid-bin Haris ne hamein hadis bayan ki : hamein Hisham ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se hadis bayan ki : hamein abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : umra usi ka hai jisey hiba kya gaya hai."
4194,"Muaz bin Hisham ne hamein hadis bayan ki : mujhey mere walid ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se hadis bayan ki : hamein abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, padhi. usi ki manind (tarah) ."
4195,"Ahmed bin Yunus ne hamein hadis bayan ki : hamein Zuhair ne hadis bayan ki : hamein abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai, wo uski nisbat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf kar rahe they."
4196,"neez Yahya-bin-Yahya ne hamein hadis bayan ki. padhi. alfaz unhi ke hain. padhi. hamein abu-Khaisma ne abu-Zubair se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : apne amwaal apne paas rokey rakho aur unhein kharaab na karo, kyonke jisne bataur umra koi cheez di to wo usi ki hai jisey di gaee hai, wo zinda ho ya Marwa , aur uske waarison ki hai. (yani jab usko aur uske waarison ko di gaee ya ghair muaqqat di gaee. ("
4197,"Hajjaj-bin abu-Usman , Sufiyan aur Ayub sab ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki. padhi. aagey abu-Khaisma ki hadis ke ham mana hai. Ayub ki hadis mein kuchh izafa hai, unhon-ne kaha : Ansar ne muhajireen ko umr bhar ke liye dena shuru kya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : apne amwaal apne paas rakho ."
4198,"ibne-Juraij ne hamein khabar di, mujhey abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : Madina mein aik aurat ne apne betey ko apna baagh bataur umra diya, phir wo faut ho gaya aur uske baad wo bhi faut ho gaee, us ( ladkey ( ne aulad chhodi aur uske bhai bhi they jo bataur umra dene wali aurat ke betey they, to bataur umra dene wali aurat ki aulad ne kaha : baagh hamein wapas mil gaya aur jisey bataur umra hiba kya gaya tha iske beton ne kaha : zindagi aur maut donon Suraton mein wo hamarey bap hi ka hai. chunanche wo Hazrat Usman ke aazad karda ghulam Tariq ke paas (jo Abdul-Malik bin Marwan ki taraf se Madiney ka governer tha) jhagdaa lekar gaey, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulaya to unhon-ne umra ki baabat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ke farman ( par gawahi di ke wo iske ( maujooda ( Malik ka hai. Tariq ne usi ke mutabiq faisla kya, phir unhon-ne Abdul-Malik ki taraf likha aur unhein us waqiey ki itlaa di aur Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki gawahi ke barey mein bhi bataya to Abdul-Malik ne kaha : Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne sach kaha, to Tariq ne us ( hukm ( ko Nafiz kar diya, chunanche wo baagh aaj tak usi ke beton ke paas hai jisey bataur umra diya gaya tha."
4199,Sulaiman-bin-Yasar se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki hui Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ke qaul ki bina par Tariq ne umra ka faisla waaris ke haq mein kya tha.
4200,"Shoba ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Qatada se suna, wo ata ke waastey se Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kar rahe they, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : umra jaaiz hai. (ye Atiya durust hai aur aagey chalta hai.)"
4201,"Saeed ne hamein Qatada se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne ata se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : umra iske khandan (main se wiraasat ke haqdaaron ( ki meeraas hai."
4202,"Shoba ne hamein Qatada se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne nazar bin Anas se, unhon-ne Bashir bin Nuhaik se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : umra durust hai."
4203,"Saeed ne hamein Qatada se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, albatta unhon ( Qatada ( ne kaha : iske khandan ki wiraasat kaha ya jaaiz kaha."
